              Returns a value of true if the always_on attribute of a  library
              signal  pin is set to true indicating that the library cell sig-
              nal pin is an always-on pin.

              Return type: boolean

              For example,

              get_property [get_lib_pins sc_cmoslp/AO22X/I1] is_always_on

       is_isolated
              Returns a value of true if the is_isolated attribute  of  a  li-
              brary signal pin is set to true indicating that the library cell
              signal pin is an internally isolated pin.

              Return type: boolean

              For example,

              get_property [get_lib_pins sc_cmoslp/AO22X/I1] is_isolated

       is_isolation_cell_data
              Returns a value of true if the isolation_cell_data_pin attribute
