              Return type: boolean

              For example,

              get_property    [get_lib_pins    sc_cmoslp/AO22X/I1]   is_isola-
              tion_cell_enable

       is_level_shifter_data
              Returns a value of true if the level_shifter_data_pin  attribute
              of  a library signal pin is set to true, indicating that the li-
              brary cell signal pin is a data pin of a  library  level-shifter
