              Return type: boolean

              For example,

              get_property          [get_lib_pins          sc_cmoslp/AO22X/I1]
              is_power_switch_enable

       is_retention_cell_enable
              Returns a value of true if the retention_pin attribute of a sig-
              nal pin is defined.

              Return type: boolean

              For example,

              get_property    [get_lib_pins    sc_cmoslp/AO22X/I1]   is_reten-
              tion_cell_enable

       output_signal_level
              Returns the power rail name/signal that is defined for a library
