              Return Type: boolean

       is_level_shifter_enable
              Returns  true  if  the  instance signal pin corresponding to the
              level_shifter_enable_pin attribute of a library  signal  pin  is
              set  to  true,  indicating that the library cell signal pin is a
              enable pin of an isolation library cell.

