              library.

              For example,

              get_property [get_pins <pin_name>] is_isolation_cell_enable

              Return Type: boolean

       is_level_shifter_data
              Returns true if the instance signal  pin  corresponding  to  the
              level_shifter_data_pin  attribute of a library signal pin is set
              to true, indicating that the library cell signal pin is  a  data
              pin of an isolation library cell.

