              * The  following  example  shows if a real or generated clock is
                defined on the pins or ports:

                tempus > create_clock [get_ports {CLK_t}]  -name  clk  -period
                100 -waveform {0 50}

                tempus > create_generated_clock -divide_by 2 -source CLK -name
                d_2 CLK_b

                tempus > get_property [get_ports CLK_t] is_clock_root

                true

                tempus > get_property [get_pins CLK_b] is_clock_root

                true

